"standard-address)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../docs/en/public-address/subaddress.md:119
#, no-wrap
msgid "Caveats"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../docs/en/public-address/subaddress.md:123
msgid ""
"It is not recommended to sweep all the balances of subaddress to standard "
"address in a single transaction. That links the subaddresses together on the "
"blockchain. However, this only concerns privacy against specific sender and "
"the situation will never get worse than not using subaddresses in the first "
"place. If you need to join funds while preserving maximum privacy do it with "
"individual transactions (one per subaddress)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../docs/en/public-address/subaddress.md:123
